P_GetCPUFPU
===========

Parameter
---------


Temps
-----


Results
-------

#cpu 		(available CPU)
		-1 = unknown
		 0 = 68000
		 1 = 68010
		 2 = 68020
		 3 = 68030
		 4 = 68040
		 5 = 68060
#cpu_str	(available CPU as string: 68000,68010,68020,68030,68040,68060)
